Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.70,0:00:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.38,0:00:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.35,0:00:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.09,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.96,0:00:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.60,0:00:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.01,0:01:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.22,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.58,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.16,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.20,0:01:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我考上的是三流私立大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.88,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我總算成為大學生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.58,0:01:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著應該是過著\N快樂的大學生活,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,字是這麼拼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.31,0:02:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要鬧了!\N明天我有模擬考!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,五代,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你,回去唸補習班吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.11,0:02:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#06 春天的衝擊!響子的秘密!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為你在打瞌睡\N沒想到突然站起來大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明天有模擬考!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經是大學生了\N居然還在作重考生時代的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.41,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你的重考生生活\N真的很悲慘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你醒著嗎?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,就算是春天\N也不能老是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最近每晚都睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會睡不著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,都是管理員不讓我睡好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五…五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,難道你跟那個美女管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還是每天晚上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒不了你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傻了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到現在連管理員的手\N都還沒牽過耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你為什麼說是她不讓你睡好的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她每晚都出現在我的夢中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢得正好的時候就醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後就半睡半醒的\N矇矇朧朧到天亮睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還真淒慘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至…至少想牽牽她的手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我已經上了大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天到了,櫻花也綻放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有季節改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的完全沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天你回來得真早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,因為下午停課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳出來散步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,因為惣一郎缺乏運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有這麼幽靜的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛才都沒有人經過耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以亂吃那個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.47,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得我好像被她拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,你也真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,這麼說來就快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來了,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在等妳耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.75,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員室的電話從剛才響個不停\N會不會是什麼重要的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎\N惣一郎拜託你照顧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟管理員在一起啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經是大學生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底什麼時候妳才會記住啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟管理員出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個問題問得非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底去了哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在一條幽靜無人的小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溜狗散步對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它還有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是我看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看錯什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前些時候我還以為\N管理員對你有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果考完試之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她根本對你不理不睬嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,這對母子真叫人討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯\N我就知道是妳打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個星期天嗎?\N好,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼等妳來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有改變的只有你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.29,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電話啊,電話\N有什麼重要的事,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老公…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的,下星期天\N一刻館的房東聽說要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?房東?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不知道會不會稍微乖一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,我跟妳說\N事情不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下星期天房東聽說要來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾年沒來的房東特地跑來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說房東要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔你個頭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房東到底要來做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房租我都有按時繳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能只是隨便來看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.99,0:12:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N我們告訴五代一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣\N你覺得如何?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有聽到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹嘛聚集到我的房間來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道房東來做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定是來趕走惡房客的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是要調漲房租\N沒有必要特地跑來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是這棟公寓太破舊了\N想改建成新大樓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個星期天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題的星期天到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一成不變的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.30,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生了一件\N宛如被芥末嗆到的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.48,0:13:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是簽房租契約時的那個老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是房東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少對我來說是個震撼事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸…爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來妳是房東的女兒啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺其中有陰謀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.01,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳該不會是來\N暗中調查惡房客的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不會搬出這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.31,0:14:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心裡有鬼的人\N才會說出這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯父?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是那位重考生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯父,我已經是大學生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又叫他伯父了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子在幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.57,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,不要站在這裡說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就進去休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子也進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用,我在這裡等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥陪妳玩吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子,不要麻煩人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係啦\N聽大人講話也蠻無聊的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.26,0:14:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,不好意思\N麻煩你陪她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那麼我們上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍馬屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼伯父嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天真的到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.19,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看起來氣色不錯,我放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為在這裡可以轉換心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.07,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是,因為這裡怪人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,一定是這個緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,坐墊給妳,還有可樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.01,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝,大哥哥你好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代我向樓下的爸爸問好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是他的孫女喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爺爺腰不好,所以要我陪他來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,妳是管理員的姪女嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害,猜對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳今年幾歲了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.87,0:16:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,12歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這麼年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看起來有那麼成熟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳感覺蠻成熟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,管理員她幾歲呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子嬸嬸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃到腰了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天氣變暖和了所以我就很放心\N好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你出門會不會太勉強了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.11,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,妳想去見惣一郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子,爸爸的腰又痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?\N都已經來到這裡了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你們不介意的話\N讓我陪你們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.41,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶好耶,跟我們一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.79,0:17:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果打擾你們全家團聚\N那我就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是不想麻煩一個外人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外人?太見外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.57,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我叫您一聲爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道妳跟他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸你別亂說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉,難得的星期天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.12,0:18:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬸嬸,他好像對我有意思喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他對我好溫柔喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是當真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你再怎麼親切\N我也不會把孫女嫁給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你出了社會\N再來我家正式拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是來掃墓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水這樣夠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子,過去好好祭拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.91,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你也去上個香好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是\N畢竟這也是一種緣分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問,這是哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…妳先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳丈夫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,我的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我兒子惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得對響子來說真的很殘忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.83,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫁過來還不到半年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才半年的時間\N惣一郎就過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的到這裡就可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.17,0:21:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的,上坡之後還要迴轉\N很麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧妳的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.32,0:22:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人如果還活著\N或許會漸漸發現很多缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.83,0:22:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,死去的人是天下無敵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且,只在一起生活半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.33,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們之間的回憶在她內心\N逐漸擴大成為她的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.34,0:22:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.61,0:23:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,千萬不能逃避現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的惣一郎已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會變成一個好男人\N保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.56,0:23:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要好好地往前看,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著前方向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.53,0:23:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好地看著前方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.05,0:23:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,走路要看著前方才行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.35,0:23:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我丈夫的名字叫惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.80,0:23:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他永遠活在我的心裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『五代煩惱不已!響子喜歡的人』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.91,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎\N和你一起度過的快樂時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.85,0:24:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.00,0:24:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.31,0:24:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.31,0:24:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.45,0:24:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.59,0:24:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.20,0:25:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.61,0:25:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.12,0:25:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛苦的折磨

